.TH StdScopes 3 "Last change: 27 May 2000" "Release 0.5" "Ulm's Oberon System"
.SH NAME
StdScopes \- standard implementation of \fIScopes(3)\fP
.SH SYNOPSIS
.Pg
PROCEDURE Create(VAR scope: Scopes.Scope);
.Pe
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I StdScopes
provides a standard implementation of \fIScopes(3)\fP that uses hashes
to store its entries and \fICompilerErrors(3)\fP for the generation
of error events.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.Tb CompilerErrors(3)
.Tp CompilerErrors(3)
generation of error events
.Tp Scopes(3)
general abstraction for scopes
.Te
.SH BUGS
.I StdScopes
is not suited for scopes containing more than 10,000 entries because
of its static hash table size.
